ir</a>\r\nEditorial — <a href="http://jenniferarmbrust.com" target="_blank">Jennifer Armbrust</a>', 'Credits/Thanks', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '21-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-04-28 17:57:51', '2015-04-28 17:57:51', '', 21, 'http://local.studiococreate.com:8888/21-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
