(390, 1, '2015-05-28 20:38:07', '2015-05-28 20:38:07', '			<h1 style="text-align: center;">Credits</h1>\r\n		<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-22 " style="height: 95px;" src="http://womenco-create.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/logo-black-300x300.png" alt="logo-black" height="95"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Studio Co/Create</strong> is a shared creative workspace in northeast&nbsp;Portland. Making. Meeting. Creating. Being.&nbsp;<br>Together.</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-25" style="display: block; height: 95px;" src="http://womenco-create.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/widmer.png" alt="widmer"></p><p style="text-align: left;">Since 1984, <strong>Widmer Brothers</strong> has been handcrafting award winning beers with a unique and unconventional twist on traditional styles, pleasing a wide range of craft beer lovers.</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://nemodesign.com" target="_blank"><img class="alignnone wp-image-386 size-full" style="height: 95px;" src="http://local.studiococreate.com:8888/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/nemo_logo2-e1432844601619.jpg" alt="" width="95" height="95"></a></p><p style="text-align: left;"><strong><a title="Nemo Design" href="http://nemodesign.com" target="_blank">Nemo Design</a>&nbsp;</strong>Portland-based brand design agency providing modern marketing for the world’s leading sport, technology and lifestyle brands</p><h3><strong>SPECIAL THANKS</strong></h3><p>Thanks to <a href="http://widmerbrothers.com" target="_blank">Widmer</a>, our generous ongoing sponsors. To everyone, past and present, at Studio Co/Create. And to all our Women Co/Create volunteers and studio hosts!</p><h3><strong>SITE CREDITS</strong></h3><p>Design — <a title="Cary Design Group" href="http://www.carydesigngroup.com" target="_blank">Cary Design Group</a>, <a title="Scout &amp; Co." href="http://scoutandco.com" target="_blank">Scout &amp; Co</a>.<br> Photography —