(184, 1, '2013-09-12 21:20:44', '2013-09-12 21:20:44', '<p style="text-align: center;">There are thousands of talented creative women hard at work in Portland,\r\nbut sometimes it''s hard for us to see each other.\r\nAnd sometimes it''s hard for others to see us, too.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">The women of Studio Co/Create are hosting\r\nLadies'' Happy Hour\r\nto remedy this, at least for a day.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">We believe in the power of numbers and collaborative creativity.\r\nWe love sharing experience, expertise, insights and resources.\r\nWe are excited to see old friends and colleagues and build new relationships.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">There will be beverages.\r\nThere will be name tags.\r\nThere will be laughter.\r\n\r\nThere will be smart &amp; clever female designers, developers, photographers,\r\ncopywriters, videographers, producers and other creatives, hanging out.\r\n\r\nTogether.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em><strong>Please, join us.</strong></em>\r\n<strong> THURSDAY, OCTOBER 10, 2013. 4 to 6 pm @ PNCA</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Women Co-Create Happy Hour will be followed by the </em>\r\n<a href="http://www.designweekportland.com/events/designing-women-panel-discussion-and-pecha-kucha" target="_blank"><em>Designing Women Panel Discussion</em></a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-150" alt="" src="http://womenco-create.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/CoCreate_300x300.gif" width="94" height="94" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Converse. Connect. Create.</em></p>', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-12 21:20:44', '2013-09-12 21:20:44', '', 2, 'http://womenco-create.com/2-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
