(248, 2, '2014-03-07 01:31:32', '2014-03-07 01:31:32', '<p style="text-align: center;">Thank you to our generous sponsors—</p>\r\n[one_third]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.grandcentralbakery.com" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter size-thumbnail wp-image-119" title="www.grandcentralbakery.com" alt="" src="http://womenco-create.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/opt_grand_central_logo-150x150.gif" width="150" height="150" /></a>\r\n<strong>Grand Central Bakery</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Grand Central Bakery features a vibrant wholesale artisan bread line and a friendly collection of neighborhood bakeries in Seattle and Portland.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; color: #fff;">.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://widmerbrothers.com" target="_blank"><img class="alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-134" title="www.widmerbrothers.com" alt="" src="http://womenco-create.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/opt_widmer-brothers-logo-150x150.jpg" width="150" height="150" /></a>\r\n<strong>Widmer Brothers</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Since 1984, Widmer Brothers has been handcrafting award winning beers with a unique and unconventional twist on traditional styles, pleasing a wide range of craft beer lovers.</p>\r\n[/one_third][one_third]<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.fieldworkflowers.com/"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-244" alt="o" src="http://womenco-create.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/o-300x300.jpg" width="150" height="150" /></a>\r\n<strong>Fieldwork Flowers</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Fieldwork Flowers was founded by Megan Arambul-Ficken in 2009. Megan''s approach to curating Fieldwork''s floral selection is to only hand-pick the healthiest, locally grown flowers in mass amounts with a limited variety as to avoid sensory overload. You can visit Fieldwork at its new South Waterfront location at 3143 SW Moody Avenue. </p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; color: #fff;">.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.organicnationspirits.com" target="_blank"><img class="alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-98" title="www.organicnationspirits.com" alt="" src="http://womenco-create.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/opt_onlogo-150x150.jpg" width="150" height="150" /></a>\r\n<strong>Organic Nation</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Ashland-Cascade Peaks Spirits Distillery. Home of Organic Nation Vodka and Gin. Woman-owned business proudly operating in Ashland, Oregon.</p>\r\n[/one_third][one_third]<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://purplehandswine.com" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter size-thumbnail wp-image-196" alt="opt_purplehands" src="http://womenco-create.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/opt_purplehands-150x150.jpg" width="150" height="150" /></a>\r\n<strong>Purple Hands</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Purple Hands winery strives for the expression of genuine inherent terroir of soil and grape. We cut our teeth with the finest, most talented winemakers in Oregon and abroad.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; color: #fff;">.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.metalcraftfabrication.com/" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter size-thumbnail wp-image-213" alt="www.metalcraftfabrication.com" src="http://womenco-create.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/Metalcraft-Fabrication_logo_WEB2-150x150.jpg" width="150" height="150" /></a>\r\n<strong>Metalcraft Fabrication</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">The Metalcraft Fabrication team specializes in building custom handcrafted equipment for the craft brewing industry. Passion for their work is reflected in the quality of their products.</p>\r\n[/one_third]', 'Thank You', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '12-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-07 01:31:32', '2014-03-07 01:31:32', '', 12, 'http://womenco-create.com/12-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
